  "body": "Hi.\r\nI would like to know how to make a fork chain of ethereum network.\r\nFirst, I won't use an snapshot of ether mainnet.\r\nI would just know the code of \r\n1. The code that includes ethereum mainnet&testnet chain id&port\r\n2. The code that includes ethereum chain's data dir(where it saves ethereum blockchain)\r\n3. and the api of ethereum mainnet\r\n\r\nAlso I would like to know \"What ethereum's network id do\"\r\n\r\nThanks",
